    dc:description "Figure 1. Phalangodus andresi sp. nov. Male holotype (ICN-Ao- 1908) A habitus, dorsal view B lateral view. Female paratype (ICN-Ao- 1909): C dorsal view D lateral view. Scale bars: 3 mm." ;
